data.description: Enjoy the Colorado lifestyle with Boyd Lake State Park, Loveland trails, and 3 lakes close by! Tired of cookie cutter homes?  This Builder's Custom home is a must see!  Situated on a corner lot with mature landscaping and wrap around front porch with wood accents, enjoy the beautiful yard or head inside where cathedral ceilings and a stone fireplace welcome you.   Upgraded solid knotty alder doors and trim are throughout the home.  The main floor and kitchen have Colorado style brick and log accents, upgraded knotty hickory floors, and Tharp knotty hickory custom cabinets.  Is a main floor primary suite on your checklist?  Welcome home, and enjoy the main floor laundry too.  The finished basement has 3 conforming bedrooms, a full bath,  family room, and a second laundry room.  AND, lots of storage!  The second floor provides a huge rec room with wet bar, and separate study/office, 2 additional bedrooms and a full bath. AND, lots of storage! Want a GREAT garage?  Check!  Oversize 3 car garage with 10' 3rd bay garage door, storage space for tools, 220 outlet and RV dump.  New 98% efficiency HVAC in 2022, new roof in 2021,  new Apex Triple Pane High E Windows throughout main and upper floor with 30 year warranty installed in 2023, and newer appliances! The multiple closets have custom built-ins for maximum storage and efficiency.   HOA provides access to 3 lakes and their parks.  A Home Warranty is also included.  This home is waiting for you to make it your own!
